
These should NOT be inside `.gitignore`.

Your final `.gitignore` should look exactly like this:

:::writing{variant="document" id="41827"}
```gitignore id="b0rzmk"
# Logs
logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
lerna-debug.log*

# Node
node_modules/
frontend/node_modules/

# Build
dist/
dist-ssr/

# Local env files
*.local
.env

# Editor
.vscode/*
!.vscode/extensions.json
.idea/

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Visual Studio
*.suo
*.ntvs*
*.njsproj
*.sln
*.sw?

# Python virtual env
myenv/
venv/
env/
.venv/

# Python cache
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]

# Django
db.sqlite3
media/
staticfiles/